name: Emotions from the sky by Daniel Vi

metadata.name: Harmony over fire
metadata.description: The hot springs of Hveravellir always cause great admiration: the color of its waters, the medicinal properties of the place and its surroundings are simply fascinating. Although underground there is a bustling geothermal activity that causes the water to boil, observed from the sky it seems to be in total harmony with the volcanic landscape.
